# 3. Most important rule to avoid frontend-backend connection errors

Both sides must agree on the **contract** before coding too much.

That means both people must agree on:
- exact API endpoints
- request format
- response JSON format
- file names / field names
- error format

If you do not agree on this early, integration will break even if both sides code correctly.

