# 9. How the graphs should behave

## Velocity graph
- x-axis = time in seconds
- y-axis = average velocity
- one line per video
- hover tooltip should show:
  - video name
  - exact time
  - exact velocity

## Clustering graph
- x-axis = time in seconds
- y-axis = clustering percentage
- one line per video
- hover tooltip should show exact values

## Comparison on same axis
If 2 or 3 videos are uploaded, all should be shown on the same graph.
This is important for easy comparison during presentation.

## Interactivity on mouse movement
What you described means:
- when mouse moves over the graph, a tooltip should appear
- the tooltip should display the value at that point
- the highlighted point should move with the mouse

This is standard in Recharts and is beginner-friendly.

